I've been looking for a tasty fish entree which is easy enough to make any day of the week, and this might be it! I took suggestions from the previous reviews and squeezed lemon on top instead of the butter. Also, as the store did not have salmon steaks today, and I don't have a grill pan, I bought fillets and broiled them for about 10 minutes. Turned out excellent. I served it with Red Potatoes and Wilted (Mustard) Greens, found on Epicurious as well. Great combination, and took me 45 minutes tops!

